Package: ws4sql
Title: Read from a ws4sql API instance (which serves JSON over HTTP)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Markus",
           family = "Skyttner",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "markussk@kth.se")
Description: The ws4sql server allows remote clients to issue web transactions such as 
    queries against a slim REST API providing JSON over http(s), where the data is backed
    by database engines such as sqlite and duckdb. This R package provides a function to 
    issue queries to such remote API instances and get results back in tabular form. 
